I think its unfair AD champs get dedicated items for all classes while AP champs all share the same items for 3 classes....

The misconception that there are simply more AD champs than AP is not true. There are almost the same amount of AP champs in the game as AD. Take a look at the list

http://guidescroll.com/2014/08/lol-champions-summary-list/


Does no one at riot think this is unfair? The worst part is the fact that they also wanted to add spear of shojin and Atmas....while AP players have been begging for better itemization for a long time.
